ingredients.ingredient: 1 (15.25 ounce) package cake mix with candy bits (such as Pillsbury® Funfetti®), or more to taste

cookingTips: Use room temperature eggs for better incorporation
Don't overmix the dough to keep cookies tender
Chill dough for 30 minutes before baking for better shape retention
enrichment.coachingPrompt: Help the user understand that boxed cake mix already contains leavening, so these cookies will be thick and cake-like. Suggest not overbaking to maintain moisture.
